      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Yes @matthaeus, it is exactly the feature I expected when needing to access org.springframework.core.env.Environment: <code>@Component public class SpringAppEnv{ public static Environment _env; @Autowired     public void setEnv(Environment env) {_env = env;}  }</code>"
